dimensions.Product: string (SDK or client type, derived from userAgent; e.g., .Net Code-gen, Java Fluent Lite, Python-SDK, Go-SDK, JavaScript RLC, Rust, etc.)
dimensions.Track: string (SDK generation track, Track1 or Track2, derived from userAgent)
dimensions.OS: string (Operating system parsed from userAgent; e.g., Windows, Linux, MacOS, Unknown)
dimensions.targetResourceProvider: string (Azure resource provider, e.g., microsoft.compute, microsoft.storage)
dimensions.Resource: string (resource type parsed from operationName, e.g., virtualmachines, storageaccounts)
dimensions.httpMethod: string (HTTP method of request, e.g., GET, PUT, POST)
dimensions.LanguageVersion: string (Language runtime version extracted from userAgent; e.g., Python 3.9.7, Java 11.0.17, .NET 6.0, Node v16.14.2, Go 1.18)

metrics.counts: int (number of requests summarized by group)

timeRange.startDateTime: datetime (calculated start time of query window)
timeRange.endDateTime: datetime (calculated end time of query window)
